ch th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tranh ch\u1ea5p<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat\/#Chi_ap_dung_cho_tran_dau_chinh_thuc\" >Ch\u1ec9 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat\/#Ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat\/\">Lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft<\/a> l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu khi c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng di\u1ec5n ra. C\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea. N\u1eafm r\u00f5 c\u00e1c quy t\u1eafc chi ti\u1ebft khi tham gia \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0 t\u1ea1i <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">Vs368<\/a> qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tong_quan_ve_luat_chap_ga_cua_sat\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng quy \u0111\u1ecbnh quan tr\u1ecdng trong b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n ch\u1ecdi g\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7n d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eeda s\u1eaft. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00ean s\u1ebd cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch gi\u1eefa hai ch\u00fa g\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4146\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4146\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4146 size-full\" title=\"T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Sv368\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-4.jpg\" alt=\"T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Sv368\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-4.jpg?v=1736061002 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-4-300x150.jpg?v=1736061002 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-4-768x384.jpg?v=1736061002 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4146\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Sv368<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, <\/span><b>lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ho\u1eb7c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1edd v\u1eady m\u00e0 s\u01b0 k\u00ea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong ph\u1ea1m vi an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c n\u1ed9i quy c\u1ea7n bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai b\u00ean tham gia gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u1ed5n th\u1ecfa.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cac_yeu_to_trong_luat_chap_ga_cua_sat\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 trong lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Theo <\/span><b>lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd n\u1eafm r\u00f5 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00fa g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi m\u00e0 game th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm r\u00f5 nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ve_phan_cua_cua_ga_choi\"><\/span><b>V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n c\u1ef1a c\u1ee7a g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn binh m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 c\u1eeda d\u00e0i th\u00ec b\u00ean y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1a. V\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 y\u1ebfu t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mang l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1eeda s\u1eaft th\u00ec hai b\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4143\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4143\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4143 size-full\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh trong lu\u1eadt\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-1.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh trong lu\u1eadt\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-1.jpg?v=1736061000 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-1-300x150.jpg?v=1736061000 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-1-768x384.jpg?v=1736061000 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4143\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh trong lu\u1eadt<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Trong_luong_cua_chien_ke\"><\/span><b>Tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fa g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 th\u00ec s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Do \u0111\u00f3, b\u00ean c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n th\u00ec s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p th\u00eam \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp cho quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Thoi_gian_tham_gia_giai_dau\"><\/span><b>Th\u1eddi gian tham gia gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00f4i khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n gi\u1eefa hai ch\u00fa g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u00ean y\u1ebfu c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng th\u00ec <\/span><b>lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fa g\u00e0 y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4145\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4145\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4145 size-full\" title=\"Th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u01a1n\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-3.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u01a1n\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-3.jpg?v=1736061001 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-3-300x150.jpg?v=1736061001 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-3-768x384.jpg?v=1736061001 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4145\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u01a1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mot_so_luu_y_can_nam_trong_luat_chap_ga_cua_sat\"><\/span><b>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm trong lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi tham gia c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0, s\u01b0 k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t m\u00e0 c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd trong <\/span><b>lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Thoa_thuan_ro_rang_truoc_khi_thi_dau\"><\/span><b>Th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, hai b\u00ean n\u00ean th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0. Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5p, c\u1ef1a c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea, th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng\u2026.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Qua \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap hai b\u1ea1n tham gia tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 tranh c\u00e3i khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Nh\u1eefng quy \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng khai v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 minh b\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dua_ra_cach_thuc_giai_quyet_tranh_chap\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u01b0a ra c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tranh ch\u1ea5p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p x\u1ea3y ra vi\u1ec7c tranh ch\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t th\u00ec hai b\u00ean c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u1ed5n th\u1ecfa. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n bao g\u1ed3m tham kh\u1ea3o tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, nh\u1eefng ai c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. Sau \u0111\u00f3, hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 x\u1eed cho \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4144\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4144\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4144 size-full\" title=\"M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm trong lu\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-2.jpg\" alt=\"M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm trong lu\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-2.jpg?v=1736061001 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-2-300x150.jpg?v=1736061001 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/luat-chap-ga-cua-sat-2-768x384.jpg?v=1736061001 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4144\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm trong lu\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chi_ap_dung_cho_tran_dau_chinh_thuc\"><\/span><b>Ch\u1ec9 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1eefng quy \u0111\u1ecbnh trong <\/span><b>lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c di\u1ec5n ra. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. Trong c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 d\u1eady gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c ch\u1eafc d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft chia s\u1ebb to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i dung li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn <\/span><b>lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. C\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n. H\u00e3y tu\u00e2n theo quy t\u1eafc v\u00e0 tham gia tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0 uy t\u00edn t\u1ea1i Sv368.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Lu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5p g\u00e0 c\u1ef1a s\u1eaft l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu khi c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng di\u1ec5n ra. C\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea. N\u1eafm r\u00f5 c\u00e1c quy t\u1eafc chi ti\u1ebft khi [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4144,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[6],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4142","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-da-ga"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4142","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4142"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4142\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5940,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4142\/revisions\/5940"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4144"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4142"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4142"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4142"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}